\id COL - Kuna, San Blas - Bible -Panama 2014 (DBL -2014)
\h Colosenses
\toc1 Colosas-Dulemarse-Narmaklesad-Garda
\toc2 Colosenses
\toc3 Col
\mt1 COLOSAS-DULEMARSE-NARMAKLESAD-GARDA
\mt2 COLOSENSES
\imt2 GEBE-SOGLENAID
\imt1 Garda-nug
\ip Pablo, Romaʼgi esgaryagi-mellesigu, gwenadgan-Colosas-neggweburgi-bukmaladse we-garda narmaksado. Colosas-neggwebur, Frigia-yargi siid. Binsamardo, we-garda birga 60ʼgi narmakles-insaye.
\is1 Colosas-Dulemarse-Narmaklesad-Gardagi weyob sunmaklenaid
\ip Gwenadgan-Colosasʼginmalad gebesailagi dule-Epafrasʼye-nugadba Bab-Jesús-abingasmalad. A-sorbali, na war-wargwen Bab-igar-oakalobi guarmalad. Bab-Dummadse-goledyobi baliwiturmarse gordii guarmalad. Pablo, Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaledbali we-gardagi gwenadganga sogsiido, melle dukin igar-mesmaloye. Melle we-ibmar ebugoye, melle we-ibmarmar gunnoye, melle we-ibmarmarse warmakoye.
\ip Jesús, we-belagwapa-ibmarmar-obinnilesad e-ibedye, degi, Jesúsʼba ibmarmar obinnilesbarye, degine, bela Jesús-sogedba ibmarmar selemaibarye.
\ip We-gardagine, weyob ilemakar sunmaklenaid:
\io1 1. Gebe-sikwas-soglenaid (1:1-8).
\io1 2. Bab-Dummadgi-abonoleged-igar (1:9-14).
\io1 3. Cristo, bur-dule-dummadid (1:15-23).
\io1 4. Pablo-e-arbasad (1:24–2:5).
\io1 5. Cristoʼgi burba-dulad-amileged (2:6–4:6).
\io1 6. Napi-soglenaid (4:7-18).
\ip Be itogua.
\c 1
\ms1 1. GEBE-SIKWAS-SOGLENAID
\mr (1:1-8)
\p 
\v 1 Ani Pablo, Bab-Dummad-sogedba Jesucristo-e-sapin-bur-dummadga gumogadid. Gwenad-Timoteo anbo,
\v 2 gwenadgan Colosas-neggweburgi Cristoʼba-nanaidse, degi, gwenadgan-gwen-galakudisurmaladse, we-garda anmar barmisiid:
\p Bab-Dummad anmar-Baba, degi, Bab-Jesucristo, bemargi nued binsamarsun, degi, ulubgi-bogidik bemar-itogega-imakbarsun.
\s1 Pablo, Bab-Dummadga dog-nuedye soged
\p 
\v 3 Anmar bemarga Babse-goled-irba, Bab-Dummadga, anmar-Bab-Jesucristo-e-Babga dog-nuedye sogdaed.
\v 4 Ar anmar be-itomalad, bemarde Cristo-Jesúsʼgi nue-bensurmarye, degi, Jesucristoʼba-nanaimalad nue-sabmarbarye.
\v 5 Ar bemar deyob gudimalad, ar ade, bemar nibneggi-megmaloed nue-bensuli edarbedimalad. Ar we-nibneggi-megmaloed nue-bensuli bemar edarbedimaladi, bato bemar Gayaburba-Nued-napiragwadba wisgusmalad.
\v 6 Ar we-Bab-Dummad-Gayaburba-Nued bemarse mosad. We-Gayaburba-Nued gebe bemar itononimargu, bemar nue mag itosmalad, Bab-Dummad bemar-abonoge-wilubsulinad. Emigindi, na e nabir-bemargi-binsaedba bemar-abonononikid. Deyobi, a-Gayaburba-Nued bela we-napneggi nasgumaid, degi, bemar-abonolesadyobi, dule-baigan abonolemaimogad.
\v 7 Anmarba-arbaed-Epafrasʼye-nugad, an nue-sabmalad, weyobi we-igargi bemar-odurdaksad. Epafrasʼde bemar-abargi Cristoʼga gwen galakusuli arbanaid.
\v 8 Epafras anmarga sognonikid, Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaledba bemarde na muchub-muchub nue-sabmarye.
\ms1 2. BAB-DUMMADGI-ABONOLEGED-IGAR
\mr (1:9-14)
\p 
\v 9 A-ulale, anmar degi-itosad-akale, anmar bemarga Bab-Dummadse-goled gwen iedisulid. Anmar bega Bab-Dummadse egisdisunnad, bitigi bemar Bab-Dummad-e-binsamaid gatik magar itosmalana gadinye, degi, Bab-Burba-Isligwaled nue-binsaed-nikagued-uked, degi, burbar-ibmar-mag-bela-itoged-uked, bemar nikusbalina gadinye.
\v 10 Adi, bemar nabir Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-daed-sunnadyob nanamalagar. Unnila Bab-Dummad-ibmar-yeerdakedbi-imakdii gumalagar. We-obared, ibmar-nuegan-imaked-oyodii guedye, degine, Bab-Dummad-bur-gatik-wisgumai guedye.
\v 11 Anmar Bab-Dummadse bemarga egisbalid, na e-gangued-gandikidbali be-ogannomarye, adi, bemar bonigan-dummagan-abin gandikidgi, degi, baisur-itogedgi gwisgumalagar.
\v 12 Bemar Bab-Dummadga weligwaledgi dog-nuedye sogmaloed. Ar Bab-Dummad anmarga igar-egasad, adi, anmar nabir Bab-Dummad-gwallu-meegwad-neggi Jesucristoʼba-nanaimalad-e-ibmar-abingamaloed abingamarmogagar.
\v 13 Bab-Dummad nia-saila-anmar-ganikidgi anmar-onononikid. Geb E-Machi-sabed-negdakmaidse anmar-odosad.
\v 14 Jesucristo na e-abe-aryosadgi anmarga isgued nabosad, anmarga isgued elinonikid.
\ms1 3. CRISTO, BUR-DULE-DUMMADID
\mr (1:15-23)
\q1 
\v 15 Cristo-Jesús, Bab-Dummad-akudakleged-e-wilub gued,
\q2 Cristo-Jesús bela ibmar-obinnilesad-iduar bato gudibinned.
\q1 
\v 16 Ar Cristoʼgi belagwapa ibmar-nibneggined, ibmar-napneggined,
\q2 ibmar mag-dakleged, degi, ibmar-akudakleged, obinnilesad.
\q1 Deginbali, burbar-dummagan-gangi-bukmalad,
\q2 burbar-dummagan-negsemamaid,
\q1 burbar-dummaganga-mamaid,
\q2 degi, burbar-gandikidba-gangued-nikmaladse-bakale,
\q2 bela Cristoʼgi, degi, Cristoʼga obinnilesad.
\q1 
\v 17 Cristo bato bela we-ibmar-iduale, gudiid,
\q2 Cristoʼgi bela ibmar nabir selemaid.
\q1 
\v 18 Cristo, eba-nanaimalad-danar-ambikunonidamalad-e-nonoga gued,
\q2 wemar Cristo-sanye sogleged.
\q1 Ar Cristo, gebesailadid,
\q2 e-inse burgwismalad-abargi gannar durgusadid.
\q2 Adi, Cristo na e-inse bela-ibmar-iduedga guegar.
\q1 
\v 19 Ar Bab-Dummad na e-abegedbali, bela Cristoʼga na Bab-Dummadga-gued uksad.
\q2 
\v 20 Bab-Dummad, Cristoʼgi bela ibmar-we-napneggined,
\q1 degi, ibmar-nibneggined, na ebo igar-naboged imaksad.
\q2 Bab-Dummad Cristo-e-abe-nakrusgi-aryonai-gusadba igar nabononikid.
\p 
\v 21 Iduale, bemar be-binsaedgi-gudiidbali, degi, ibmar-isgana-imakdiidbali, Bab-Dummadgi bangus gudimalanad, degi, bemar e-isdaradmarbalinad.
\v 22 Emigindi, Bab-Dummad, Cristo-dulega-imaksadgi, nakrusgi-burgwenai-gusadba bemarbo igar nabononikid. Deyob Bab-Dummad imaksad, adi, bemar swilidiki, gwen gutu-naisuli, degi, begi dule-ibmar-akar-soged-sate, Bab-Dummad-asabin gwisgumalagar.
\v 23 Ar deyob be gumalaga, bemar Bab-Jesúsʼgi-bensulidgi gandikidba, ise-sakdigale, degi, sikirmaksuli, alamaknai gumalargebed. Degi, Bab-Dummad-Gayaburba-Nued-be-abonogedgi, be bangusur-gudii gumalargebed. We-Gayaburba-Nued bemar itosad, degi, we-napneg-naidgi bela dulemarga egi sunmaklenaid. Ani, Pablo, we-igar-barsogegala an nugsalenonikid.
\ms1 4. PABLO-E-ARBASAD
\mr (1:24–2:5)
\s1 Pablo-e-arbasad
\p 
\v 24 Emigindi, an bemar-ular-wilediidgi an weligwar itoged. Ar deyobi, Cristoʼba-nanaimalad-danar-ambikunonidamaladga, Cristo-wileged-yoo-bergued an-sangi an wiledisunnad.
\v 25 Bemar-bendakega, Bab-Dummad, Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-danar-ambikunonidamalad-e-maiga-guega an-sunonikid. Bab-Dummad e-Gayaburbagi-sunmakega an-barmisad.
\v 26 We-Gayaburba bela dikasurgus, degi, gebe-dula-ambikusad-akale, Bab-Dummad igar-odukuar-mesisgusadgi sunmaked. Emigindi, Bab-Dummad, Jesucristoʼgi-akananaimaladga a-igar magarononikid.
\v 27 Amarga, Bab-Dummad we-igar-dukuar-maidgi Judíoʼsurmaladga ibmar-nuegan-mamaid oyononisunnad. We-igar-dukuar-maidi, Cristo gued. We-Cristo bemargi-maid, a bemarga yoedse ibmar-nued-uklegoye-soglesad gued.
\p 
\v 28 Anmar we-Cristoʼgi bela dulemarga sunmakdiid, dulemar-unadiid, degi, nue-binsaed-nikaa dulemar-odurdakdiid, adi, bela dulemar Cristo-Jesúsʼgi isgussuliyob Bab-Dummadga oyogegar.
\v 29 A-ular, Cristo na bela e-gangued-anga-ukedba an arbanaid, degi, an alamaknaibalid.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Ar bemar nue-wisgubi an abedo. An bemarga, degi, Laodicea-neggweburgi-bukmaladga, deginbali, dulemar-amba yoo-an-wagar-dakmaladga an nue-dummad alamaknaid.
\v 2 An alamaknaid, adi, bemar niga-gangumalaga, bemar bulakwaa sabguedgi nanamalaga, degine, bemar bela mag-itogedgine, Bab-Dummad-igar-dukuar-maigusad, nuekwaa wisguegar. Ar we-igar-dukuarmai-gusad, Cristo-sunnad gued.
\v 3 Bela Cristoʼginbi binsaed-nuegan-mamaid, degi, ibmar-mag-itogued danikid.
\v 4 Ar we an bemarga sogdo, adi, bemar mer dulemar-yamo-binsaed-nikaa-yeer-sunmakdimaladse yardaklemalagar.
\v 5 Ar an bemar-abargi sanagwar gudisur-inigwele, an burbardi bemar-abargi gudiid. Deginbali, an weligwar itobalid, ar an bemar-wisgugu, bemarde innikii nanadimarye, degine, Cristoʼgi nue-bensuli bemar nanadimarbarye.
\ms1 5. CRISTOʼGI BURBA-DULAD-AMILEGED
\mr (2:6–4:6)
\p 
\v 6 Ar bemar Bab-Jesucristo be-Dummadga be abingasmalad. A-ulale, bemar Cristoʼgi nanamalargebed.
\v 7 Gatik bur bule Cristoʼgi-akanai, degi, egi-gandik-gwichi be gumarsun. Ar igi be-odurdaksamala, deyobi, bemar Cristoʼgi bur gatik bensuli gumala. Bab-Dummadga dog-nuedye-sogdii gumala.
\s1 Cristoʼginbi san-burba-geg-bergued danikid
\p 
\v 8 Nue salakarmar. Mer dulemar-yamo-binsa-na-ibmar-wisi-sogdimaladse binsaed galemalo. Ar wemar unnila dulemar-igar-maidba, degi, we-napneg-igar-maidba sunmakdimalad. Cristo-igar-maidba sunmakdisurmalad.
\p 
\v 9 Ar Cristoʼgi bela Bab-Dummad-gued sanar dakleged.
\v 10 Ar Cristoʼgi bemar unnitiba e-gangued nikad. Cristoʼgi Bab-Dummad na e-gangued-itogega bemar-imaked. Ar Cristo, bela burbar-gangued-nikamalad-e-dummadid, degi, burbar-gandikidba-sunna-ibmar-imakmalad-e-dummadbalid.
\v 11 Deginbali, bemar Cristoʼgi burbar abgan-e-uka-duku siklesmalad. Dule deyobi be-imaksasurmalad. Bab-Dummad-sunnad Cristoʼgi-bemar-oakasgu, deyob be-imaksamalad. Deyobi, be-san-isguedgi be-ollor-imaknonimalad.
\v 12 Ar bemar Bab-diigi-ogleged-igar-imaksamargu, Cristoʼba napa-urba diglesmalad. Deginbali, bemar Bab-Dummad na e-ganguedgi gannar Cristo-odulosadgi bengussurmarsoggu, bemar Cristoʼba burbar gannar durgunonikid.
\p 
\v 13 Bemar burbar abgan-e-uka-duku-sikleged-yoo-imaklegua, bemar na be-isguedgi burgwar gudimalanad. Ar emigindi, Bab-Dummad Cristoʼgi-bemar-oakasgu, bemarga san-burba-dulad uksad, degi, bemarga bela be-isgued elisad.
\v 14 Anmar Igar-Maidgi-annadigusad-ular, anmarga sabsur-odurdakleged-igar mainad. Ar Bab-Dummaddi, Cristo-nakrusgi-burgwenonigu, anmarga sabsur-odurdakleged-igar-maidi, osulosad.
\v 15 Bab-Dummad bela burbar-gangued-nikamalad-e-gangued, degi, burbar-gandikidba-sunna-ibmar-imakmalad-e-gangued obelosad. Bab-Dummad bela dulemar-wagab, Cristo nakrusgi burgwisgua, we-burbamar-ibgwensuli imaksad, degi, egi nakwisbalid.
\p 
\v 16 Degisoggu, be-ibmar-gunnedgi, igi, be-gobedgindibe, be-ibagan-dakedgindibe, nii-binid-ibagi, igi, obunnoged-ibagindibe, dulemar mer begi sunmakmalo.
\v 17 Ar belagwapa wemar yoo-ibmar-danikoed-e-burbagan gued. Ar Cristoʼgi ibmar-napiragwad maid.
\v 18 Dulemar-na-yamo-san-bipi-imakdimalad, degi, baliwitur-nug-odummodimalad, mer Bab-neggi-be-ibmar-nued-maid begi sued be imako. Ar amardi, ibmar-daksasuli binsa gordiid, degi, na e-galagwensuli-binsaedba san-odummodimalad.
\v 19 Amardi, Cristoʼgi gwen akanaisurmalad. Ar Cristoʼdi na e-ibmar-imakedbali, bela egi-akananaimalad, san-dubamar-mamaidba-nasgumaiyob, nasgumai imaked, degi, Bab-Dummad-igar-mesisadba, bela-dulemar-egi-akananaimalad oatoed.
\p 
\v 20 Ar bemar Cristoʼba bato burgwismalale, we-napneg-e-igar-mamaidba bar be gudisurmalad. Ar degite, ¿ibiga bemar amba we-napneg-e-igar-weyob-mamaidba be damala?
\v 21 We-igar-weyob-sogmaidba: “Mer be ebugo, mer be gunno, mer be be-argangi suo.”
\p 
\v 22 We-igargan, unnila dulemar-sogedba, degi, dulemar-igar-odurdakedba mamaid. E-gangued-nika-maid ibagan-nadapidbali, bergumai guoed.
\v 23 Ar napiragwad, we-ibmar igar-nuedyob dakleged, ar ade, dule-wiledakedgi, na san-bipi-imakedgi, degi, sabsur na-san-saedgi dule-odurdaked. Ar degi-inigwele, we-ibmarmar anmar-isgubiedgi geg anmar-bendaked.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Ar bemar bato Cristoʼba gannar durgussoggu, nibneggined-ibmarmar be amimar, ar bia Cristo Bab-Dummad-argan-nuedsik sii.
\v 2 Nibneggined-ibmargi bur be binsamar, mer we-napaneggined-ibmargi be binsamar.
\v 3 Ar bemar bato burgwismarsoggu, emigindi, Bab-Dummad bemar Cristoʼba-gudiguega be-imaksamalad.
\v 4 Ar Cristo, bemar-san-burba-dula-imaknonikid, we-napnegse-danikile, bemar eba e-gangued-yeerdaklegedba danimarmogoed.
\s1 Igar-sered, degi, igar-binid
\p 
\v 5 Degisoggu, belagwapa bemargi wemar-napneggined-ibmar-naid be osulomar:
\q2 Abirgunagwarsuli negsichigi galagwensuli-daed,
\q2 ibmar-isgana-imaked,
\q2 yogasaar igarsuli-daed,
\q2 isgued-imakedgi-binsaed,
\q2 degi, ibmarbina-surbinsa-itoged.
\q3 Ar dule deyob itogele, we-ibmar na e-bab-dummadga imakdiid.
\p 
\v 6 A-ulale, dule-uayasatedamalad, Bab-Dummad-dule-sabsur-odurdaked-e-igar itononidamalad.
\p 
\v 7 Bemar epenne we-igargangi nanadii gusmalad. Deun, bemar we-igargan-sogedba gudigusgu.
\v 8 Emigindi, bela we-igargan be indakmarba: Urwed, sae-itoged, isdar-dulemargi-binsaed, dulemargi-gakansaar-sunmaked, degi, galagwensuli-nisaar sunmaked.
\v 9 Mer na ga be gakansamar, ar bemarde bato epenne-be-damalad osulosmalad.
\v 10 Emigindi, bemar burba-binidgi gudimalad. We-burba e-obinnisad-Bab-Dummadyob-guedse, bur bule gatik Bab-Dummad-wisguedse gwagmaioed.
\v 11 We-burba-binidgine bar binsalesulid, we-dule, Griego-duleye, Judío-duleye, abgan-e-uka-duku-sikaledye, abgan-uka-duku-sikarsulidye, dule-ainebalidye, dule-ibmar-gwen-wissulidye, dule-maiga-gudiidye, degi, dule-maiga-gudisulidye. Bela wemar, Cristoʼgi emarbi gued, degi, Cristo bela wemargi maidbibalid.
\p 
\v 12 Bab-Dummad bemar-sabed, degi, bemar-susbalid, adi, bemar egadga gumalagar. Degisoggu, nue-emar-wiledake be nanamar, igar-nuegangi-nanadii be gumar, na san-bipi-imakdii be damar, binnalegwadgi ibmar-imakdii be imakmar, degi, ukurmakar ibmar-imaksuli be nanamar.
\v 13 Na be muchub-muchub ibmar-akalar, baisur-itoged be imakmar. Ar dule-wargwen dule-baidgi akar-ibmar-sogele, igi-barsaye be sogmar. Ar igi Cristo be-isgued bega osulosa, deyobi, bemar na be muchub-muchub igi-barsaye sogmarmo.
\v 14 Wemar-ukine, bur bule, bemar sabedgi nanamar, ar ade, sabguedi, bela egi ibmar gwamaklesiid.
\p 
\v 15 Cristo-bogidik-nikad be-ulubgi-nikagudii be gumar. Ar bemar unnila wargwenna-guega, Bab-Dummad bemarse gochad. Bemar, Bab-Dummadga dog-nuedye sogmar.
\v 16 Cristo-gayaburba bela-bela bemar-gwagegi-nai be imakmarsun. Nue-binsaed-nikaa na be muchub-muchub odurdakmar, degi, na be muchub-muchub binsaed-dakmarba. Gwagegi doggus-nuedye-sogedgi, be Bab-Dummadga ega-namaklegedmar, namaklemalad-nuegan, degi, burbar-namaklemalad namakmar.
\v 17 Ar bela be ibmar-imaked, degi, bela be ibmar-soged, bela Bab-Jesús-nuggi be imakmar. Jesús-nuggi Bab-Dummadga be doggus-nuedye sogmar.
\s1 Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad igi-damalargebe
\p 
\v 18 Omegan, be-sui-urbaligwa be nanamar. Ar bemar Bab-Jesúsʼba naimarsoggu, deyob be nanamalargebed.
\p 
\v 19 Suigan, be-ome be nue sabgumar, mer be sabsur-imako.
\p 
\v 20 Mimmigan, be-babganba bela be ibsamalo, ar deyob be damalale, Bab-Dummad yeer-itodaed.
\p 
\v 21 Babgan, mer be be-mimmigan-ourwed imakmar, adi, mer ibmar-imakbisuli gumalagar.
\p 
\v 22 Maigan, bela be-dummagan-we-napnegginmalad bega ibmar-sogedba be damar. Yamo uaya-nikaa be damarye benik sogmalaga, mer be unnila be-daknaidginbi deyob be damalo. Suli, amba be-daksulile, gwage-napiragwadgi be ibmar imakmar, degi, be Bab-Dummad-dobegwa-nanaedba be ibmar imakmar.
\v 23 Ar ibu be imaknaimardibe, bela weligwaledba be imakmar. Bab-Jesucristoʼga ibmar-imaknaiyob be imakmar, dulemarga imaknaisuliyob.
\v 24 Ar Bab-Jesús bemarga-ibmar-ukoye-sogsadi, bato bemar wisid. Ar bemar Dummad-Cristoʼga arbananaid.
\v 25 Ar dule ibmar-ichakwa-imaked na e-ibmar-imaksadba sabsur-odurdaklegoed. Ar ade, Bab-Dummadi bela dule emarbi daked.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Dummagan, bemar be-maigan nue-igar-nikaa, degi, napiragwadgi be nimalo. Ar bemar insamarmogo, bemar nibneggi Dummad nikamarmogad.
\s1 Odurdakleged-baigan
\p 
\v 2 Bab-Dummadse gatik be gormar. Gatik nue be atakmar, degi, Bab-Dummadga dog-nuedye be sogmar.
\v 3 Deginbali, Bab-Dummadse be anmarga gormarmogo, adi, Bab-Dummad, E-Gayaburba-Nuedgi-sunmakega nabir anmarga yawagak-egaega, degi, anmar Cristo-igar-dukuar-maigusad osanalogegar. Ar a-Gayaburbagi an sunmakdiid-ular, an emidi, esgaryagi mellesiid.
\v 4 Bab-Dummadse gormala, adi, an Cristo-igar-dukuar-maigusad nue-bakarmakar an osanalogega.
\v 5 Dulemar-Bab-Dummadba-naisurmalad-abargi, nue-binsaed-nikaa be nanamar. Cristoʼgi-sunmaked-e-iba-nagunonikile, be sunmako.
\v 6 Nuedgi, degi, nabir-itolegedgi be sunmakdii gumar. Deyob geb be wisgumaloed, igi nabir bemar dulemar-abinsaoe.
\ms1 6. NAPI-SOGLENAID
\mr (4:7-18)
\s1 Degimaloye napi-sogsiid
\p 
\v 7 Anmar-gwenad-sabed-Tíquico, Bab-Jesúsʼgi innikigwadba-arbadiid, degi, nue-an-bendakdiid, bemarga bela an gudiid sogdapoed.
\v 8 Ar a-ular, an bemarse Tíquico barmisiid, adi, bemarga sogega, igi anmar wegi gudii, degi, bemar-ogannomarbaligar.
\v 9 Tíquicoʼba bemar-neggined-Onésimoʼye-nugad nadapid. Onésimoʼde, anmar-gwenad-sabedid, degi, Bab-Igargi innikigwadba nanadiidid. Wemar-ebogwad bela bemarga sogdapmaloed, igi an wegi gudimala.
\p 
\v 10 Aristarco, anbo-esgaryagi-mellesiid, degi, Marcos, Bernabé-e-niga bemarga sogsimalad, bemarde, nued sogeye. Marcosʼgi bato an bemarga sunmaksa gusad. Ar bemarse ataknadele, bemar nue abindakmalo.
\v 11 Deginbali, Jesús, Justoʼye-bimarbalid, bemarga sogsimogad, bemarde nued-sogeye. Bela Judíoʼmar-Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-abargi, unnila wemarbi Bab-Dummad-e-negdakmaid-igar-onasguedgi anba arbasmalad. Wemar nue-an-ogannodimalad.
\v 12 Bemar-sorda-wargwen-Epafrasʼye-nugad bemarga sogsiid, bemarde, nued sogeye. We-Epafras, Cristo-maiga-gudiid, bemarga Bab-Dummadse nue-gordiid, adi, bemar bensuli, degi, gandikidgi, mer galakumalaga, Bab-Dummad-sogedba bela bemar ibmar-imakmalagar.
\v 13 An-sunnad an nue wisid, igi Epafras bela-bela bemarga, Laodiceaʼginmaladga, degi, Hierápolis-neggweburgi-bukmaladga bela-bela-alamanaid.
\v 14 Ina-duled-Lucas, anmar nue-sabed, degi, Demas, bemarga sogsimalad, bemarde, nued-sogeye.
\v 15 Gwenadgan-Laodicea-neggweburgi-bukmaladga, Ninfasʼga, degi, e-negyagi Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-danar-ambikunonidamaladga be sogmalo, bemarde, nued-sogeye.
\p 
\v 16 Bemar we-garda-absosad-sorba, Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-danar-Laodicea-neggweburgi-ambikunonidamaladse be barmidoed, adi, amar we-garda absomarmogagar. Bemar, an Laodiceaʼse-garda-barmisad absomarmogoed.
\p 
\v 17 Arquipoʼga be sogmalo, Bab-Jesúsʼgi be arbaed-abingasad be imakye.
\p 
\v 18 Ani Pablo, an-argan-sunnadgi napi an bemarga narmaked, bemar nued sogeye. Be insao, an esgaryagi mellesiid. Bab-Dummad nued bemargi binsamaloed. Be itomargua.
